.
Yet God is still such a loving, patient Father, so full of mercy & grace toward me. His Holy Spirit helps me every step of the way. I feel His tender loving care in so many ways. 
.
I have 2 recent testimonies. I was recently struggling with a desicion. I felt something inside of me telling me to do the opposite of what I had made up my mind to do. It did not make sense to me. But I decided to obey & follow the voice inside because I knew that was the Holy Spirit telling me to stop & not move forward. I did not understand why! But I know from RECENT experience that if I feel that unrest about something, even if it doesn't make LOGICAL sense, follow what that voice inside of me says because it's the Holy Spirit. It's easy to miss the Holy Spirit talking to us if we aren't tuning in to it. So this time, I decided to focus. Lord & behold, a few days later I found out what a HUGE mistake I would've made had I not followed that tugging of the Holy Spirit. The still small voice. The LORD really protected me & my family! I'm just so grateful & blown away by His kindness & mercy!! 
.
Now, in those days when I struggled with that desicion, I asked God to reveal Himself to me, to reveal who He is to me. This was an "exercise" for a worship dance video I saw because I want to learn, so I did it. That night, God spoke to me in a dream & He told me that He is the one who takes care of me. 😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭
.
I'm just so grateful to God. Beyond words 😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻 Praise His Holy name!!!!! 💕💕💕💕💕💕💕💕💕💕💖💖💖💖💖💖🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻💃💃💃💃💃
